AngularJSVue.js Vue.js Vue 

<div id="app">

    {{price1 | price}}

    {{price2 | price("$")}

    {{price3 | price("",4)}}

</div>

<script>

    "use strict"

    var app = new Vue({

        el:"#app",

        data:{

            price1:18,

            price2:19.5,

            price3:23.25

        },

        //

        filters:{

            //:(1,...){

            //    return ;

            //}

            price:function(text,prefix,count){

                prefix = prefix || "";

                if(count == 0){

                    count = 0;

                }else{

                    count = count || 2;

                }

                text = parseFloat(text).toFixed(count);

                text = prefix + text;

                return text;

            }

        }

    });

</script>

<script>

    "use strict"

    var app = new Vue({

        el:"#app",

        data:{

            user:{},

            respData:{}

        },

        methods:{

            submit:function(){

                $.get("http://127.0.0.1",this.user,function(data){

                    this.respData = data;

                }.bind(this),"json");

            }

        }

    });

</script>

"use strict";

var app = new Vue({

    el:"#app",

    data:{

        i:0,

        respData:{}

    },

    //

    // 0  i 

    beforeCreate(){

        //Vueappthis

        console.log("beforeCreate ",this.i);

        this.i = 2;

        console.log("beforeCreate ",this.i);

    },

    // 0  i 

    created(){

        console.log("created ",this.i);

        this.i = 3;

        console.log("created ",this.i);

    }

});

<div id="app">

    <my-component1></my-component1>

    <my-component2></my-component2>

<script>

    "use strict"



    //

    var bus = new Vue();



    var myTemplate1 = {

        template:"<button type='button' @click='sendMessage()'>1</button>",

        methods:{

            sendMessage:function(){

                //

                bus.$emit("message1","aaabbb");

            }

        }

    }

    var myTemplate2 = {

        template:"<div>{{message}}</div>",

        data:function(){

            return {

                message:""

            }

        },      

        created(){

            //created

            bus.$on("message1",function(m){

                this.message = m;

            }.bind(this))

        }

    }



    Vue.component("my-component1",myTemplate1);

    Vue.component("my-component2",myTemplate2);

    var app = new Vue({

        el:"#app"

    });

</script>
